des:
Timeplus Q. A.

This skill allows the user to answer a series of questions based on whether the user had a meeting with an existing client or a new client. At the end, the skill collates all the questions and answers in an email and sends it to the user's email ID.


This skill is developed by VoiceTech Labs.

Version: 3.0
Published: November 13, 2020.
